change his decision, isn't it?

521
00:48:43,041 --> 00:48:46,290
My decision won't change.
But, times will.

522
00:48:47,250 --> 00:48:48,332
Anything could
happen tomorrow itself.

523
00:48:49,416 --> 00:48:52,582
