644
00:56:43,166 --> 00:56:46,499
Take it all back,
neighbours have begun to ask.

645
00:56:46,583 --> 00:56:47,832
Sir, I can understand.
But until the..

646
00:56:47,916 --> 00:56:50,499
..market opens I can't
take the goods back.

647
00:56:50,833 --> 00:56:52,040
