661
00:57:35,833 --> 00:57:55,749
Glory to Guru!

662
00:57:55,833 --> 00:57:58,749
You are great.
- Wonderful.

663
00:57:59,291 --> 00:58:03,374
Brother Guru,
you've done a great job.

664
00:58:08,291 --> 00:58:11,832
