667
00:58:20,416 --> 00:58:23,624
You forgot the lame Jalkukdi?

668
00:58:25,750 --> 00:58:26,832
Close your eyes.

669
00:58:39,500 --> 00:58:41,499
Don't open them. Don't open them.

670
00:58:44,333 --> 00:58:45,415
