1203
01:44:21,916 --> 01:44:23,499
You know what I'm talking about.

1204
01:44:25,416 --> 01:44:28,165
They're after your blood.

1205
01:44:28,333 --> 01:44:29,415
So?

1206
01:44:30,833 --> 01:44:39,582
